        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-数据导入导出"><a href="#1-数据导入导出" class="headerlink" title="1.数据导入导出"></a>1.数据导入导出</h1><h2 id="1-1导入csv"><a href="#1-1导入csv" class="headerlink" title="1.1导入csv"></a>1.1导入csv</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pandas.read_csv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/image-20211121211059421-16379149995731.png"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">usecols=[0,1,2,3]表示从csv文件第一列取到第四列</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/image-20211121211807189-16379150428773.png"></p><h2 id="1-2导入Excel"><a href="#1-2导入Excel" class="headerlink" title="1.2导入Excel"></a>1.2导入Excel</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pandas.read_excel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/image-20211121211707893-16379150152912.png"></p><h2 id="1-3导出csv、excel"><a href="#1-3导出csv、excel" class="headerlink" title="1.3导出csv、excel"></a>1.3导出csv、excel</h2><p><img src="/images/image-20211121212234383-16379150758994.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
